title: Football Manager 2009 Superpack (Facepack ,Logos)
description:
Football Manager 2009 Huge Pack. Contains almost all europe's logos and faces and some american logos and most faces.
Enjoy.

To install it:
1) Go to your documents.
2)Open Sports Interactive folder
3)Open Football Manager 2009 Folder
4)Extract the Zip there
5)Run the game
6)In preferences go to Display and sound
and untick "use skin Cache" and tick always re-load skin on confirm.
You are ready.. Enjoy.
